	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The only way bards get mana is from AAXP (max of 4 regen - 3 from MC and 1 from B&amp;MRejuv) and FT (max of 15, like all FT items). That combined with a natural regen of 1 per tick maxes out at 20 mana per tick. Bard meditate skill caps at 1, it gives no mana regen bonus but allows us to memorize songs faster.<br><br>Bards use mana for our only AE DD that is ranged, our two higher charm songs, and our &quot;Fading Memories&quot; AA. FM is like FD but superior. =)<br><br>Bards get their mana from INT. INT and MANA items are important to bards, as are FT items.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
